Installation instructions

== Requirements ==

Build:
 * autotools
 * make
 * any C compiler such as gcc, cmake, or tcc

Runtime:
 * any libc with syscall(2) syscall

== Build ==

From a tarball:
 $ tar xvjf libsignalfd-X.Y.Z.tar.bz2
 $ cd libsignalfd-X.Y.Z/
 $ ./configure [options]
 $ make
 $ make install

From the source repository:
 $ git clone <url>
 $ cd libsignalfd/
 $ ./autogen.sh [options]
 $ make
 $ make install

You may get help about available options with:
 $ ./autogen.sh --help
or:
 $ ./configure --help

